23d665e --><h3>Basis for recommendation</h3><!-- end field e9fae402-e9a2-4c30-822f-2238123d665e -->","summary":null,"htmlStringContent":"<!-- begin item df88e135-d216-4ca3-89e0-912555fda0ec --><!-- begin field df5c5958-95ab-4ecb-b4cc-9f4cea9f8cf8 --><p>The information on the differential diagnoses of haemorrhoids is based on expert opinion in review articles on anorectal conditions [<a class=\"bibliography-reference internal-reference\" href=\"/topics/haemorrhoids/references/\">Orkin et al, 1999</a>; <a class=\"bibliography-reference internal-reference\" href=\"/topics/haemorrhoids/references/\">Friedman et al, 2002</a>; <a class=\"bibliography-reference internal-reference\" href=\"/topics/haemorrhoids/references/\">Fleury, 2011</a>; <a class=\"bibliography-reference internal-reference\" href=\"/topics/haemorrhoids/references/\">Zagrodnik, 2011</a>; <a class=\"bibliography-reference internal-reference\" href=\"/topics/haemorrhoids/references/\">Sanchez and Chinn, 2011</a>; <a class=\"bibliography-reference internal-reference\" href=\"/topics/haemorrhoids/references/\">Lohsiriwat, 2012</a>; <a class=\"bibliography-reference internal-reference\" href=\"/topics/haemorrhoids/references/\">Iqbal et al, 2013</a>; <a class=\"bibliography-reference internal-reference\" href=\"/topics/haemorrhoids/references/\">BMJ, 2016</a>].</p><!-- end field df5c5958-95ab-4ecb-b4cc-9f4cea9f8cf8 --><!-- end item df88e135-d216-4ca3-89e0-912555fda0ec -->","subChapters":[]}]}}},"staticQueryHashes":["3666801979"]}